    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Mini Bash 里拳打、抓取、甩飞你的朋友！和好友一起在线或本地游玩这款混乱的物理派对斗殴游戏！大笑、痛哭，然后再也别和他们说话！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>随心所欲地玩！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本地最多支持 4 人，在线最多支持 8 人——无论怎么玩，记得一定要交几个仇人！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>炸飞你的朋友！</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/543e486291a5707e50ee136ec185a681.poster.avif?t=1752535534\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/543e486291a5707e50ee136ec185a681.webm?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/543e486291a5707e50ee136ec185a681.mp4?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>彻底毁灭你的朋友</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拳打、抓取、抛掷、跳舞、爆炸、攀爬、大笑、痛哭，拼尽全力冲上排行榜顶端！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>疯了！疯了！</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/b8e583a8169e0fe1d3f3ebc25676a5f9.poster.avif?t=1752535534\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/b8e583a8169e0fe1d3f3ebc25676a5f9.webm?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/b8e583a8169e0fe1d3f3ebc25676a5f9.mp4?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>争夺宝石！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在桌游模式中角逐，看看谁才是你们之中最坏的一个！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>亮晶晶！</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/53fbe8a6cae11f096dbc1100f1ac7cf9.poster.avif?t=1752535534\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/53fbe8a6cae11f096dbc1100f1ac7cf9.webm?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/53fbe8a6cae11f096dbc1100f1ac7cf9.mp4?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>称霸王座！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>看着你那些所谓的朋友落败，尽情享受胜利的滋味！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>你是最强的！</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/3584d76cb8c0e97037578a80fa375e13.poster.avif?t=1752535534\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/3584d76cb8c0e97037578a80fa375e13.webm?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113730/extras/3584d76cb8c0e97037578a80fa375e13.mp4?t=1752535534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></h2></h2></h2>",
